skins.name: Original
skins.lore: Raised in the deepest jungle, Nidalee is a master tracker who can shapeshift into a ferocious cougar at will. Neither wholly woman nor beast, she viciously defends her territory from any and all trespassers, with carefully placed traps and deft spear throws. She cripples her quarry before pouncing on them in feline form—the lucky few who survive tell tales of a wild woman with razor-sharp instincts, and even sharper claws...

skins.name: Snow Bunny
skins.lore: A fierce warrior who makes her home in the winter forest, Nidalee has little interest in Snowdown parties. Instead, she prefers to spend her time protecting cheerful woodland creatures from trappers and intruders, giving her furry friends a reason for the season.

skins.name: Leopard
skins.lore: Nidalee roams the tall grasses and bubbling tar pits of her home, a prehistoric savannah teeming with natural magic. She protects her leap of leopards by taking the appearance of their hunters, deceiving and disarming human threats with her wild skill.

skins.name: French Maid
skins.lore: Armed with a diverting maid outfit, a sunny disposition, and a vast knowledge of cleaning techniques, Nidalee catburgles her wealthy customers without them being any the wiser. She does it all for her kitties, who have grown used to some very high quality scratching posts.

skins.name: Pharaoh
skins.lore: Worshiped as a god-queen of the Great Desert, Nidalee is the avatar of the glorious cat-god, Sypakaa. As war tears through the land, Nidalee will do whatever it takes to protect her city and her temple from those who would dare threaten them.

skins.name: Bewitching
skins.lore: She is a cat. That is a hat. Legally, we're not allowed to put those two thoughts together.

skins.name: Headhunter
skins.lore: There are those who still ask: between man and beast, who is the better hunter? With her alien biology allowing her to embody both, Nidalee of the Headhunters answers that question with, “I am.”

skins.name: Warring Kingdoms
skins.lore: Of the legends surrounding Nidalee, it is difficult to know what is true and what is mere myth. Some within the Warring Kingdoms say she fights with the wild ferocity of a white tiger, that the tiger's spirit dwells within her heart. Others believe she is the white tiger, that she can become the beast itself.

descriptions.description: Loot exclusive gained during the 2019 MSI Event.

skins.name: Super Galaxy
skins.lore: Of the new class of Super Galaxy cadets, Nidalee—with her exceptional skill for throwing projectiles through zero-gravity—shows the most promise. As the Spider Queen continues her reign of terror, the team will need Nidalee's cunning tactics and keen hunting instincts if they want to save the galaxy.

skins.name: Dawnbringer

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a Loot exclusive in 2019.
This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2019.

skins.lore: Both a celestial beast and a dawn-walking primordial, Nidalee rules over the restorative calm of the natural world. She guards the land's remaining peaceful places, bringing light and order to the mortal creatures under her care.

skins.name: Cosmic Huntress

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2020.

skins.lore: A cosmic tracker and ferocious hunter, Nidalee travels the galaxy in an eternal hunt, shifting her shape to hide among the sky's wandering stars. Tasked with finding and caring for newborn stars, she is dedicated to defending them from the ever hungry Dark Star corruptants.

skins.name: DWG

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive during MSI 2021.

skins.lore: Honoring Canyon's winning performance as Nidalee during the 2020 World Championship.

skins.name: Ocean Song

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2022.

skins.lore: The Ocean Song Festival is lucky to have Nidalee as its performer stylist, with her fashion guides selling almost as much as her albums, but in reality she's here as a featured part of Yone's show. She was the first person he showed his lyrics to, and it's her honor to lend them her voice.

skins.name: Kittalee

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2023.

skins.lore: Adorable squeaky toy or deadly weapon? In Nidalee's claws, a Friendly Fish (TM) can be both!

skins.name: La Ilusión

descriptions.description: This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2023.
This chroma was released as a bundle exclusive in 2023.

skins.lore: A jaguar leader of her own pack, Nidalee was both feared and respected by her neighboring humans. When she fell to a group of hunters for protecting her family, the shared love not just from her pack, but from her neighbors, reincarnated Nidalee as an Eidola Vida. With the power to assume both jaguar and human form now, she watches over her kin from afar.
